h1. create-unit-test-constraints-spock

h2. Purpose

The @create-unit-test-constraints-spock@ generates all the unit tests for constraints with the "Spock Framework":https://code.google.com/p/spock/

h2. Examples

{code:java}
grails create-unit-test-constraints-spock Person
grails create-unit-test-constraints-spock "*"
{code}

h2. Description

Given at least one domain class, this command creates unit tests for all the domain class constraints with the "Spock Framework":https://code.google.com/p/spock/. The command will generate one file for each class domain property.

Usage:

{code:java}
grails create-unit-test-constraints-spock [domainClass]
{code}

Arguments:
* @domainClass@ - Either a domain class name (case-sensitive) without its package or a wildcard (*). If you specify the wildcard the artifacts will be generated for all domain classes.

